description:
Elizabeth Hurley, global ambassador for the Estée Lauder Companies' Breast Cancer Campaign, explains why her work to support breast cancer research will never be done. Plus, Jenn and Jess weigh in on a viral discussion about bullying in the beauty industry and discuss a new advancement in vegan color cosmetics.
